videos.description: Prior to their matchup, the Lakers and the 76ers hold a moment of silence in honor of Kobe Bryant.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lakers, 76ers hold moment of silence for Kobe) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lakers, 76ers hold moment of silence for Kobe

videos.description: Ben Simmons drives right by the Lakers' defense for a one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons blows by Lakers defense for dunk) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons blows by Lakers' defense for dunk

videos.description: Marc Gasol bounces a pass to a driving LeBron James for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gasol feeds LeBron for the jam) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gasol feeds LeBron for the jam

videos.description: LeBron James wraps a pass around a defender to Anthony Davis for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron dishes to AD for the flush) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron dishes to AD for the flush

videos.description: Joel Embiid denies LeBron James of a layup and then on the other end, Danny Green sinks a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid's denial of LeBron leads to Green's 3-pointer) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid's denial of LeBron leads to Green's 3-pointer

videos.description: Dwight Howard air-balls a free throw, and Seth Curry can't help but smirk on the bench.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Seth Curry smirks after Howard's airball at the line) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seth Curry smirks after Howard's air ball at the line

videos.description: Ben Simmons dishes to Danny Green for a 3-pointer and then Simmons finds Tobias Harris from downtown on the next possession.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons sets up Green and Harris for back-to-back 3-pointers) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons sets up Green and Harris for back-to-back 3-pointers

videos.description: Joel Embiid is shaken up after getting fouled hard by LeBron James, who is given a flagrant 1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron gets first flagrant 1 since 2014 after hard foul on Embiid) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron gets first flagrant 1 since 2014 after hard foul on Embiid

videos.description: Joel Embiid is assessed a flagrant 1 after swiping his elbow across Anthony Davis' face.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid called for flagrant 1 on AD) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid called for flagrant 1 on AD

videos.description: Joel Embiid drives baseline and banks in a reverse layup while drawing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid drops in reverse and-1) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid drops in reverse and-1

videos.description: Joel Embiid reacts to the 76ers' 107-106 win over the Lakers on Wednesday and provides an update on his back after a hard fall.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Embiid wasn't worried during 76ers' thrilling win) 2021/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid wasn't worried during 76ers' thrilling win

videos.description: The 76ers defeat the Lakers in a thrilling 107-106 game when Tobias Harris sinks the game-winning shot with 2.4 seconds left.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Harris' heroics help 76ers end the Lakers' perfect road record) 2021/01/27 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Harris' heroics help 76ers end Lakers' perfect road record

videos.description: Ben Simmons got off to a fast start in the 76ers' one-point win over the Los Angeles Lakers.

tracking.trackingName: INET_NBA Highlights (Simmons goes for triple-double in win over Lakers) 2021/01/28 PAC RIM ONLY

videos.headline: Simmons goes for triple-double in win over Lakers

videos.description: Joel Embiid reacts to LeBron James' dangerous play, which earned the Lakers' star a flagrant foul. Embiid predicts he would have been ejected if the roles were reversed.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Embiid: If I had committed that foul on LeBron, I would have been ejected) 2021/01/27

videos.headline: Embiid: If I had committed that foul on LeBron, I would have been ejected
